                        <p>All Division Policies are listed in the above "Division" section.&nbsp;The policies listed
                           in this section&nbsp;are not included under the "Division" section because they are unique
                           to the Cooperative Extension Service.</p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="Link to the Cooperative Extension Service Policy Manual" href="https://www.uaex.uada.edu/extension-policies/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span color="#0066cc">Complete Cooperative Extension Service Policy Manual</span></a></p>
                        
                        <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
                        
                        <h2><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Dale Bumpers College of Agricultural, Food and Life Sciences</strong></span></h2>
                        
                        <p>All Division Policies are listed in the above "Division" section.&nbsp;The policies listed
                           in this section&nbsp;are not included under the "Division" section because they are unique
                           to the Bumpers College.</p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 95-appendix 1 - Dean's Faculty Advisory Council Operating Document Policy and Guidelines Memorandum" href="/docs/policies/pmgs-95-a1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 95-appendix 1 - Dean's Faculty Advisory Council Operating Document Policy and
                              Guidelines Memorandum</a>&nbsp;</p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 96-01 - Harry R. Rosen Alternative Pest Control Center (RAPC) Management Policy and Users' Manual 68" href="/docs/policies/pmgs-96-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 96-01 - Harry R. Rosen Alternative Pest Control Center (RAPC) Management Policy
                              and Users' Manual 68</a></p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 60px;">Appendix A - C Forms (<a title="PDF" href="/docs/policies/forms/pmgs-96-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PDF</a> <a title="MSWord" href="/docs/policies/forms/pmgs-96-1.dot" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MSWord</a>)&nbsp;</p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 96-appendix 1 - Dale Bumpers Lifetime Achievement Award in Agricultural, Food and Life Sciences" href="/docs/policies/pmgs-96-a1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 96-appendix 1 - Dale Bumpers Lifetime Achievement Award in Agricultural, Food
                              and Life Sciences</a></p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 03-07 - Guidelines: Bumpers Scholars" href="/docs/policies/pmgs-03-7.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 03-07 - Guidelines: Bumpers Scholars</a></p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 03-10 - Form for Peer Evaluation of Faculty" href="/docs/policies/forms/pmgs-03-10.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 03-10 - Form for Peer Evaluation of Faculty</a></p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a title="PMGS 06-01 - Alumni Society Scholarship" href="/docs/policies/pmgs-06-1.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PMGS 06-01 - Alumni Society Scholarship</a>&nbsp;</p>
                        
                        <p style="padding-left: 30px;">&nbsp;</p>
                        
                        <p>PMGS = Policy and Management Guidelines Statement &nbsp;<br>PMGM = Policy and Management Guidelines Memorandum</p>
                     
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     			
                     							
                     			
